#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_leasing.catalogue
msgid ""
"Performance and design were the key words during the conception of this "
"super car. No compromises were made to keep the pleasure of driving despite "
"those constraints."
msgstr ""
"Las palabras que siempre tuvimos presentes durante la creación de este "
"increíble automóvil fueron rendimiento y diseño. No comprometimos ninguna "
"funcionalidad y logramos mantener el placer de conducir pese a ciertas "
"limitaciones."

